{"tid":378701,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[HoneyWorks]又有新動畫","createTime":"2017-08-28T16:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T12:41:59.000Z","uid":49057,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"aa460abd12bb1d9490b5275ad1f98b939b8df5b2","tid":378701,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:29:02.000Z","msg":"新作TVアニメ「いつだって僕らの恋は10センチだった。」11月24日より6週連続放送決定！「初恋の絵本」や「一分一秒君と僕の」で描かれた物語に新規要素を追加！春輝と美桜の青春を描く本作をアニメーション制作：Lay-duceでお届けします！放送をお楽しみに！<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DITyblzUIAE_usa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDITyblzUIAE_usa.jpg&h=be364ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單翻譯下<br />\n即係將繪本組既故事整成6集既動畫，11月24號開始播，故事會加入新劇情<br />\n<br />\n之前睇完劇場版真係覺得唔係太夠，唔知其他cp會唔會都出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bf6fc8e17d0e994618fc4ae77def1d8e08519d","tid":378701,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9ec7594dc6e003c3fcce3ae8315112323cb522","tid":378701,"uid":332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"日本果邊好受歡迎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d90833cc931163be2442ddac69178346aa35b0f","tid":378701,"uid":49057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日本果邊好受歡迎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以twitter作統計平台，條tweet都有7k retweet同11k個like<br />\n大概係fgo既一半<br />\n<br />\n我自己就純粹覺得d歌幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd983a63c03cd572088d4fe740d19c12e6a2693","tid":378701,"uid":22018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:08:56.000Z",